bib_record.title: Atlas of gamma-ray spectra from the inelastic scattering of reactor fast neutrons

free_txt: Elemental and enriched Pd, Sn, Te, Sm, W
IRT-M reactor for enriched Mo, Cd, Dy
We found that a Maxwellian with kT~1.4 MeV is optimum
to reproduce the 56Fe(n,n'gamma) intensities in the
atlas from the TOF measurement with the GAINS
detector array at GELINA reported in Negret et al.
Shielded by Fe (5 cm), paraffin with boron
carbide (8 cm), Pb (10 cm) and 6Li (3 mm).
to calibration and non-linearity of the spectrometric
